) 15... a5 $1 {[%cal Gb7a6,Ya5a4] Creating the direct threat of Ba6 and a5-a4
sometimes.} (15... d5 $2 {now is bad due to} 16. exd5 cxd5 17. Qf5 $1 Bd6 18.
