gxf6 $15 {immediately is similar.}) ({In case of passive play Black is more
than fine. For example:} 12. Bc4 Qe7 13. O-O O-O 14. Qd2 Rad8 15. Qe3 Rfe8 16.
Be2 (16. Rad1 $2 {loses on the spot in view of} Bxh2+ $1 17. Kxh2 Ng4+ 18. Kg1
