crushing attack already.}) (12. Be2 Rb8 $17 {is also better for Black.}) 12...
Qe7 13. Bxf6 {Muzychuk,A (2533)-Ushenina,A (2452) EU-ch (Women) 11th 2010 (11)
½-½} ({The best option for White probably was} 13. O-O-O Be5 14. Bxf6 Bxf6
15. Qd6 {but after} O-O 16. Qxe7 Bxe7 $15 {the endgame seems more pleasant for
Black due to the bishop pair.}) {In the game Muzychuk exchanged queens, but}
13... gxf6 $1 {is a nice improvement. Considering the open position and
