{[%csl Re4,Rg2]} 19. Qf3 Qxf3 20. gxf3 Bxd5 21. Bxd5 Rxb4 {with full equality.}
) 16... a5 17. h4 $1 ({It is useful to insert this before} 17. b5 Bd7 18. Nc3 (
18. Qb3 Qc8 19. Nc3 Bd8 20. Bc4 Bb6 21. O-O Qd8 $11) (18. h4 Be7 $5 19. Nc3 $6
