15. c4 (15. Nb5 Nxd5 16. Bxa5 Qxa5 17. Qxd5 exf4 18. Rxf4 Be6 $132 19. Qxb7 Qd2
) 15... Bf6 $13 {we are ready to bring the knight back to d7. Now the White
phalanx is a little broken, and it is unclear how to continue the offensive.}
16. Ra2 Nd7 17. Nb5 Nc5 18. Kh1 b6 $15 19. b4 axb4 20. Bxb4 exf4) (14. Kh1 Nc5
