{[%evp 0,19,24,18,46,46,56,21,21,43,29,29,29,29,29,29,29,29,29,29,47,21]} 1. e4
c5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. d4 cxd4 4. Nxd4 Nf6 5. Nc3 e5 6. Ndb5 d6 7. Nd5 Nxd5 8. exd5
Ne7 9. c4 Ng6 10. Qa4 Bd7 11. Qb4 Qb8 12. h4 h5 {The pawn on h5 turns out to
be a target for attack in this case, because it is not very clear what to do
with it, how to castle. However, Black has counter-resources.} 13. Be2 (13. Be3
a6 (13... b6 {- 12.Be3}) 14. Nc3 Be7 15. Na4 (15. g3 O-O 16. Be2 (16. Bd3 $6
